      "content": "it's just hard to see those \"small moments\" when it feels like i've lost all my agency. i'm just watching myself wither away. i wish i felt like i actually had a say in how this ends, rather than just being a passenger in a body that's failing me. it feels so undignified, just waiting for the inevitable.",
